data.description: I have loved the Circle Drive park neighborhood since the day I drove around Woodward neighborhoods for the first time. The whole neighborhood has a certain charm like none other. This home is no exception. Though full of modernized improvements, this is a cute "non cookie cutter" piece of 1950s charm that is few and far between. It features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, an inside utility, a HUGE sunroom that can be a great area for the kids to hang out in, all new laminate flooring, an updated kitchen, fresh paint, and even a little shed in the backyard to work in. There is a park across the street! Definitely worth looking at!!
